<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>AirBNB DyNamic Pricing</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/static/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/twitter-bootstrap/2.3.2/css/bootstrap-combined.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery.js"></script>
    <script src="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/twitter-bootstrap/2.3.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="row" style="width:1200;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="span8 offset2">
        <h1 style="text-align:center;">AirBNB DyNamic Pricing</h1>
        <p>Not sure what to charge your AirBNB guests or when to up the price? Then you have come to right place.
        <p>We will go through local hotel listings and give you a estimated price per night for your Zip Code every few days!

        <form method="post" action="/signup" >
          <legend>Sign up</legend>
          <fieldset>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email</label><input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="zipcode">Zipcode</label><input type="text" name="zip_code" pattern="(\d{5}([\-]\d{4})?)" placeholder="Zipcode of the AirBNB" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="price">Price (USD/night)</label><input type="number" min="1" max="9999" step="1" size="4" name="price" placeholder="Your base price on AirBNB" />
            </div>
            <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" value="Sign up" />
          </fieldset>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
